# Environment variables
# Never commit secrets. Only schema files (.env.example, .env.k8s.example)
# are tracked; the broad .env.* rule keeps every other variant gitignored
# (e.g. .env, .env.local, .env.docker, .env.k8s, .env.<anything>).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.k8s.example

